Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from Raira Academy\Nwas attacked by the Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you should get the others caught\Nup in fighting over her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest in Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't headless, I'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill them. I'll kill them dead!\NI'll kill them deader than dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I flew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flew?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that I wanted was to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:14.27,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a stopped clock is\Nright twice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikebukuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The source of this junktown's energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth about its greed,\Ngrowing greater by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the strongest man in the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About six months ago, when I was doing an\Narticle on the strongest man in Ikebukuro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a "Tokyo Year in Review"\Narticle, I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air around him was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're God?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shizuo, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the next place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher who can't keep\Nhis hands off his students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought back the purity that\NI felt when I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,back before I started spending my days\Nwriting for third-rate gossip magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curiosity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a strong sense of curiosity was what
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made me want to know everything\Nabout the strongest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the mess afterward made\Nme postpone my article.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the incident's details,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the whole town felt like it was\Nhaunted with little demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something was about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the strongest man would\Nsomehow be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I started my article on 'bukuro again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to gather information\Nfrom the people around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some salmon roe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't order it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo is friend! He is friends with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he talking like this deliberately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My Conversation with Russian\NSushi Employee, Simon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen him fighting or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe, don't {\i1}clam{\i0} up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, clam sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One order of clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon's a pacifist, so you can't\Ntalk with him about fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just wanted to know\Nwho the strongest is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should ask a specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shiki of the Medei Awakusu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest in Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was told you might\Nknow something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the age of street-fighting is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We use our heads now, not our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We work clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you let them\Nscrew with you, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if someone screws with us\Nor threatens our families,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether they're a little kid,\Nor they pull a knife or a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we erase 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones who fight in this\Ntown aren't pros like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like the Dollars and\Nthe Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as they don't\Nscrew with our business,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, there's been some weird\Nurban legend shit out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the Slasher and\Nthe Headless Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see... The strongest in\NIkebukuro would probably be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told he fights straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there's an information broker\Nwho knows more than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you introduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're on the subject, big guy,\Nthis article of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who told you about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Conversation with Shinjuku Information Broker,\NOrihara Izaya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um... I can't really\Nreveal my sources...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tokyo Year in Review," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys do reports on weird crimes and gangs,\Nand your next issue's on Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that much already,\Nthen that makes this easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm planning on writing about\Nthe strongest person in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of strong\Npeople in that town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sushi-seller Simon would be the\Nstrongest in a hand-to-hand fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-chan would be the strongest\Nin a street fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shizu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo. You came\Nto ask about him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Well, this Shizuo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who needs\Nto know about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I try to know about him 'cause\Nhe's trouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that bugs me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't want to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Niekawa-san,\Nhow's your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a parent, you must be worried that\Nshe transferred over such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six months ago, you talked\Nto Shizuo and ended up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,flying through the air with\Nthe greatest of lampposts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sniff around too much, and it might\Ncause problems with my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but right now, a lot of dangerous\Nstuff's going down in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:08:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the war between the Dollars\Nand the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that, and then there are the\NSlasher attacks that brought it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an uncontrollable urban legend\Nout there that I don't need anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about Heiwajima Shizuo...\NI'll introduce you to a friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The information broker, Orihara, introduced\Nme to a surprising person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and here's a warning for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about Shizu-chan's\Nbrother in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish you'd told me that six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mention of my daughter\Ncaught me off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a daughter who's in her\Nsecond year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived with her since my wife ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't believe\Nshe thinks much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the reason I started writing\Narticles just for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm the transporter, Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Conversation with Transporter Celty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Shizuo is a good friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he'd be scary if you got him mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm researching who'd be\Nthe town's strongest in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magazine seems to like that kind\Nof thing. Ranking gangs and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there are some people\Nwho say you're the strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're laughing, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Shizuo's way stronger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty scary how dangerous he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. It's not really any kind of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a wolfman or a\Ndevil or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got little grey trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, it's like the way that, no matter\Nhow good the martial artist,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a shot to the head and it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like that handgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to compare him to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This urban legend put what I'd felt, meeting\NHeiwajima Shizuo, into words perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. His strength\Nis on another level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The adrenaline in his brain probably\Nbrings out incredible power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a single instant, his power surpasses\Nhuman limits. It's truly incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, this is just\Nme being curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you show me what's\Nunder your helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you don't really have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Celty must be a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I got my nerves together,\NI continued my interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I heard about was the Dollars\Nand the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars continued to ignore\Nthe Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People said that the Yellow Scarves's leader,\Nthe "General," might make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt even the young turks\Nof the Yellow Scarves know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumors say that only the\Nveterans have seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Yellow Scarves
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gave his men strict orders to do one thing,\Nto stay away from Orihara Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he be the strongest man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Scarves seemed to attribute\Nthe Slasher attacks to the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few days ago, one high school\Ngirl was unharmed in an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made me think of my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A father, protecting his daughter from\Nthe Slasher, risking his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an alien who doesn't understand\Nher right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll face my beloved daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy the Slasher attacked was a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,reporter writing a "Year In Review"\Narticle for {\i1}Tokyo Warrior{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> A magazine writer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> Have I ever lied to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> Setton-san, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fan of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> Really? I'll check him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> The cops need to do their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}<Saika-san has joined the channel>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> They're here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> Hu-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> h?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}<Saika> Cut today
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> I'm the one who wants to cut you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> But, no... I still love strong people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> How ya doing, Saika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> It's useless, Setton-san.\NSaika won't respond to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> I'm sure I have to cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about cutting people and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's the Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> Strong people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to love them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka> What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Shizuo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> Heiwajima Heiwajima Heiwajima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I and Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's wish, Heiwajima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima, mother's wish, cut
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, Heiwajima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, Shizuo, mother's wish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}<Saika-san has left the channel>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Happy Birthday, Anri"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up, Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get fat, Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'll exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll be together forever,\Nmother, father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every night, the girl had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy family, a perfect family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a failed illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago, her parents\Ndied in a horrible incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even now, alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she still dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the happy family\N she'll never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the tragedy in which she lost her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time the Slasher\Nappeared in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:15:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri, you sure it's OK to be\Ngetting ready for field day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew she was an unfair person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew exactly what the teacher was\Nup to, but she didn't stand up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She simply withdrew into herself\Nand waited for it to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher might come after you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew that she was a parasite,\Nfeeding off them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. You were waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting so long, we thought we'd fossilize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sqrt 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Square root?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, square root?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a -20 or something\NI can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next thing I knew, I was in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay still for a while, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need about a week in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't remember things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't get up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Niekawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would watch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside me said to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekawa-san, in room five, isn't back yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope his wounds don't reopen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill! Kill! Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuo, I appreciate it, but you\Ndon't have to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee the Slasher\Nwill show up tonight, at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I hate that goddamn Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if it's a cursed\Nblade or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a sword, it'll die if I snap it in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill it, whether it dies or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill! Kill! Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Shizuo... There's no need\Nto deal with these guys right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need something, pill bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking to the cockroach over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, looks can kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's at least a 0.0000000000000000000675%\Nchance that a curse or a stare can kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, bartender?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartender...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you glare at someone, you\Ncan't complain if they kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekawa Haruna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he respond that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's eleven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a student, so go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want us to take you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,110 call, reporting several youths involved\Nin a fight, in East Ikebukuro Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head straight to the scene. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responding now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuhara-san, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, you can wait at the police\Nbox, and I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop using random kanji for things\Nand thinking it makes you badass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at the age when you want to look at
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,things differently than others,\Naren't you, Yumacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stop thinking that if you try doing\Nthings in a way that most adults hate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that kids in their rebellious\Nphase will like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so silly how people try to look cool\Nby criticizing society or ideologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't often say bad things about books.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A book he once published on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asleep, so I shouldn't talk, but\None of our guys was taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention and gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, unlike with Kazutawno,\Nit was someone we don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it was someone from the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have some empathy, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cry, but it's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hate the Slasher,\Nbut it's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you guys join the Dollars, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to live a peaceful life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get a green-haired\Nforeign daughter and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then come back and live happily,\Nnext to three beautiful sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful life that would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yotsuba&!? Yotsuba&!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is where\Nthe Slasher showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's being careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls like that will get attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, might be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy had red eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit of trauma coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ram 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Celty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful, Kadota-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said I wanted a peaceful life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-defense, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Headless Rider... And Shizuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dotachin, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Heiwajima Shizuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to meet you, Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so, so, so much, Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll interview him and write this article,\Nand everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter will come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and things will be fine\Nbetween us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like they used to-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:14.91,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,This program is a work of fiction.\NAny resemblance to people, parties,\Nor situations is purely coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.92,0:24:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should have ended\Nthe Slasher incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they weren't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, it was the beginning of her fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long, long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.76,0:24:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.44,0:24:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mutual Love.
